{"type": "article", "id": 23812, "title": "折纸雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 178, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125953Jo1ZbMS0mAXuFODQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把雨伞并没有金属骨架和金属头，它是用可回收塑料制成。手柄底部有用于旋转的弹簧装置，自动沿着伞内的塑料导向板开合，有折纸的感觉，也是极简的设计。此外，塑料材料比起传统的布料有更强的防水性。产品获得了 2015 年的红点奖，目前已完成众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/860103721/satm-the-umbrella-reimagined/description\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125948BbyILpaAdHMlDs86.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125949CsfRnKZOA3SjrYNL.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125951KUtA1cNPXdQh9WOo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61413844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125952XeaUSFdVrlMADO4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125952uObKdwVMy2pJq9gS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}